CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper May 21, 1960, pg. 20, reads: "Free Tickets - These lucky youngsters got free tickets to the boxing matches held at the Centre Avenue YMCA. Handing out the ducats are popular Fifth Ward Constable Tommy Smith... Constable Smith sponsored the show. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Tommy Smith and group of children posed in boxing ring in Centre Avenue YMCA
